Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 01:12:30 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/7] feat: Add Playback Preferences and Stremio Subtitles
 integration

- Adds Playback Preferences (Audio Lang, Sub Lang, Video Quality) to Phone App Settings.
- Sends preferences via WebSocket protocol to TV for auto-selection.
- Adds `StremioSubtitleService` to query OpenSubtitles v3 addon via IMDB ID.
- Automatically selects and passes subtitles for TMDB Library playback based on preferred language.
- Enhances `DetectedVideosSheet` with a new "Subtitles" tab and TMDB-based manual subtitle search feature.
- Reroutes Debrid file plays to `DetectedVideosSheet` first, allowing users to manually search for subtitles before sending to TV.

Co-authored-by: truedem0n <20188425+truedem0n@users.noreply.github.com>
